About
============================================================================
Colterm is python module for managing (colored) terminal input/output.

It includes helpers for changing terminal title, changing color, printing
colored output, stream handler for colored logging and helpers for constructing
prompts and menus with input validation.
Colored output works on both Linux and Windows.

Homepage:
    http://github.com/xificurk/colterm

